- `documenti.manage_categorie` to manage categories;
- `documenti.manage_collegamenti` to manage document links;
- `documenti.export` to export lists;
- `documenti.admin` to administer every document.

### If you don't see the menu entry
This usually means your role doesn't include `documenti.access`.

